<h1> Learn Bible Verses</h1>

The app comes with over 20 verses on the topic of <b>faith</b>. <br>
It also supports speech output and recognition. <br>
<br>
So you can start learning (or <i>exploring</i>) right away. <br>
And click <b>Back</b>. <br> <br>
Or click <b>Introduction</b> to get to know it better.
<br> <br> <br>
Click Welcome at the bottom of the <i>Homepage</i> to return here.